## 8. RELEASE PIPELINES

In Azure DevOps, under **Pipelines**, go to **Releases**.  
Click **New Pipeline** and select **Empty Job**.

Next, click **Add an artifact**, choose the source pipeline  
(the build pipeline created earlier), and click **Add**.

![Enter image alt description](../Images/FIt_Image_45.png)

---

Click on **Job → Tasks**.

![Enter image alt description](../Images/CYg_Image_46.png)

---

Click **“+”** and add **Azure App Service Deploy**.

![Enter image alt description](../Images/S9X_Image_47.png)

---

Select your Azure subscription.  
If authorization is required, complete the authorization process.
